singam ii ( english : lion ii ) is a 2010 indian tamil action masala film directed by hari , a sequel to singam , which stars suriya , anushka shetty , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani , hansika motwani and hansika motwani in the lead roles . the film released on 5 august 2013 .